2009-08-12  Chris Toshok  <toshok@ximian.com>

	* bitmapsource.h|cpp (SetBitmapData): add an extra parameter
	"own" (default: true) which, if true, causes the bitmap source to
	free the bitmapdata when it's destroyed.

