2009-02-11  Jeffrey Stedfast  <fejj@novell.com>

	* eventargs.h (MouseEventArgs::GetEvent): Expose the raw GdkEvent.

	* textbox.cpp (TextBoxView::ConnectBlinkTimeout): Get the cursor
	blink timeout from the GtkSettings.
