	Memory Optimization:

	* textbox.cpp (append_runs): Updated. Also fixed a bug which would
	sometimes append empty TextRuns to the list.

	* text.cpp (TextBlock::Layout): Updated. No longer need to use the
	retarded TextRun linebreak ctor.

