	hashtable can contain Value with a NULL DependencyObject

2009-01-07  Larry Ewing  <lewing@novell.com>

	* canvas.cpp:
	* frameworkelement.cpp:
	* shape.cpp: Quick hacks to get test 0 passing after the default
	value changes.

