2008-12-01  Larry Ewing  <lewing@novell.com>

	* brush.cpp, brush.h: add Fill and Stroke methods to brush so that
	we can handle image and video brush opacity properly.

	* src/control.cpp
	* src/layout.cpp
	* src/panel.cpp
	* src/shape.cpp
