	* brush.cpp (ImageBrush::SetSurface): same.

	* media.cpp: same.

	* collection.cpp (DependencyObjectCollection::SetSurface): same.
	(Collection::RemoveAtWithError): this (against logic) raises
	ArgumentException, not ArgumentOutOfRangeException.

