	* list.cpp (List::List): Init length to 0.
	(List::Clear): Reset length to 0.
	(List::Append): length++
	(List::Prepend): length++
	(List::Insert): length++
	(List::InsertBefore): length++
	(List::Unlink): length--
	(List::Length): Fixed to be O(0) instead of O(n)

