	* xaml.cpp: (expat_parser_error): translate XML_ERROR_NO_ELEMENTS
	into appropriate error code.

2008-04-03  Larry Ewing  <lewing@novell.com>

	* xaml.cpp: Generate errors when trying to set readonly properties.

